Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\DeliveryOptimization
and change the DWORD strings
DODownloadMode
SystemSettingsDownloadMode
to
0

&

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\DeliveryOptimization\Config
and change the DWORD string
DODownloadMode
to
0


Finish.
